## Quick Project Overview

### What This Project Does
Multi-service Quarkus-based cinema booking system with:
- iOS client (SwiftUI) + Web UI (AngularJS)
- 4 backend microservices (dalogin, mbook, mbooks, simple-service-webapp)
- MySQL database (dual schemas: login_ + book)
- Kubernetes infrastructure (Minikube locally)
- Braintree payment integration
- Real-time availability tracking with WebSocket

### Tech Stack at a Glance
| Component | Version | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|---------|
| Java | 17 | Backend runtime |
| Quarkus | 3.19.4 | Microservice framework |
| MySQL | 8 | Primary datastore |
| Kafka/Zookeeper | 3.x | Messaging |
| Kubernetes | Minikube | Orchestration |
| Prometheus/Grafana | 2.x / 10.x | Observability |
| Tempo | Latest | Trace collection |
| Apache | 2.4 | Reverse proxy + SSL |
| Appium | 3.x | iOS UI testing |
| Braintree | 3.36.0 (Java) | Payments |

