### Commit Convention
```
feat: add [feature name]
fix: resolve [issue]
docs: update [documentation]
chore: [maintenance]
refactor: [code cleanup]

Examples:
- feat: add Speckit constitution for AI agent context
- fix: correct pessimistic lock timeout in DAO
- docs: update payment workflow in constitution
```

